<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<link rel="stylesheet" href="CSS/signupLogin.css">
<link rel="shortcut icon" href="./Img/Logo.png" type="image/x-icon">
<script src="./External/typed.js-master/lib/typed.min.js"></script>
<script src="JS/show.js" defer></script>
<script src="JS/login.js" defer></script>
<script src="JS/loginChange.js" defer></script>
<title>The Cake Bakery</title>
</head>

<body>
<div class="goback"><a href="index" class="back">&larr;</a></div>
<div class="center">
<form class="signupContainer" action="/forgot" method="POST">
        <h1 style='color: rgb(0, 184, 0);'><%= goodtitle %></h1>
        <h1 style="color: rgb(184, 0, 0);"><%= badtitle %></h1>
    <label for="username"><input type="text" name="username" id="username" placeholder="Username"><figcaption style="margin: 0 0 -1.5rem 2px; font-size: 11px; text-align: start;" id="userfig"></figcaption></label><br>
    <label for="password"><input type="password" name="opassword" id="opassword" placeholder="Old Password"><figcaption style="margin: 0 0 -2rem 2px; font-size: 11px; text-align: start;" id="opassfig"></figcaption></label><input type="checkbox" name="showo" id="showo"><br>
    <label for="password"><input type="password" name="password" id="password" placeholder="Password"><figcaption style="margin: 0 0 -2rem 2px; font-size: 11px; text-align: start;" id="passfig"></figcaption></label><input type="checkbox" name="show" id="show"><br>
    <label for="cpassword"><input type="password" name="cpassword" id="cpassword" placeholder="Confirm Password"><figcaption style="margin: 0 0 -2rem 2px; font-size: 11px; text-align: start;" id="cpassfig"></figcaption></label><input type="checkbox" name="show" id="showp"><br><br>
    <button class="suBTN">Sign Up</button><br>
    <a href="signup" class="allogin">Don't have an account? Signup.</a>
</form>
</div>
<div class="description">
    <div class="topLg">
        <img src="IMG/logo.png" alt="logo" width="150" height="150">
        <h3>The Cake Bakery</h3>
    </div>
    <div class="cakebakeDes">
    <p>The Cake Bakery hand-make the highest quality Black Forest. Using hand-sourced ingredients from the best farmers in New Zealand,
        head baker Adityaa Mulmi employs traditional The Cake Bakery baking methods that are not commonly practiced in New Zealand. <br><br>
        
        The Cake Bakery specialises in Banana Cakes, Carrot Cakes, Cheese Cake, Black Forest. They have recently perfected their recipe for Nepali style Banana Cakes
        called ‘Banh Mi’ cakes. We supply to cafes, restaurants and hotels across the Hornby and Christchurch areas and will be opening a physical store in Riccarton soon!</p><br>
        <a href="login"><button>Already have an account? Login</button></a>
    </div>
</div>

</body>
</html>